{"success":true,"result":{"Q_10108037539403-2":{"resources":[],"questions":[{"id":"Q_10108037539403-2","subjectId":101,"knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000673226","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"resourceIds":null,"resourceIndex":0,"listenUrl":null,"listenName":null,"listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"paperIds":["P_10100121220828-1","P_10100121220828-2","P_10100121220828-3"],"books":null,"booksNew":null,"contentTypeId":1010008,"contentType2Id":0,"difficultyInt":3,"description":"阅读课外文章，回答问题","notFitMobile":0,"seconds":31,"complex":1,"nid":null,"lastEditorId":null,"finalAuditorId":null,"roughAuditorIds":null,"content":{"content":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>“多才多艺”的气象卫星</strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">①如今，浩瀚的太空中又多了一颗新星——“风云一号”气象卫星，在增强我国监测灾害性天气的能力，提高天气预报的准确性，延长预报时效方面，正起着越来越重要的作用。不仅如此，气象卫星在非气象领域也有卓越的贡献。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">②我国从1985年就开始研究利用气象卫星图资料探测森林和草原火灾的方法。经过几年的努力，现在中国气象卫星中心可以利用卫星云图照片，随时发现热源目标，能清晰地显示出森林或草原火灾发生的位置、范围和强度。  </p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">③我国海洋渔业部门利用气象卫星资料分析鱼群活动已获得成功，<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">使研究区当年的鱼产量比原来提高5～7倍。</span>根据气象卫星红外遥感资料与被测表面温度密切相关的原理，可以制作海水表层温度场分布的等值线图，也可以根据温度场的分布特征来确定或预测渔场的中心位置。这样，单是缩短渔轮在海上找鱼的航行时间，使之少费柴油一项，就可以节省大量开支。</p><p><br></p>","contentDesc":"","analysis":"","subContents":[{"content":"<p>选择。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">从全文看，本文说明的重点内容是什么？</p>","answers":[{"answer":"1","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":1,"analysis":"","optionType":"sentence","options":[{"option":"气象卫星在气象领域的卓越贡献。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"气象卫星在非气象领域的卓越贡献。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}}],"hideOptionNumber":0,"listenUrl":"","listenName":"","listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"oralDict":{